data.description: Beautiful Arlington floorplan in Creekside at Mulberry.  ASSUMABLE LOAN!!! LOCATION!!! 9 Minutes away from North Georgia Medical Center Braselton. 10 minutes from 85 and  Chateau Elan. 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. BEDROOM AND FULL BATH on main level. Soft neutral colors throughout. Office/Loft on second level. Laundry located upstairs.  Beautiful custom kitchen cabinets with quartz countertop. Gorgeous island with seating for 4.  Large walk in pantry. Farmhouse sink and upgraded range. Extra cabinets and countertop on the side for storage and a coffee station. Large covered patio for entertaining. Fenced backyard for the kiddos and furry friends. Quiet cul de sac.
